    "causal_summary": "A spec folder carries the same `trigger_phrases` concept in three separate surfaces that are never asserted to agree. The curated set lives in spec.md frontmatter, the indexed set lives in `description.json`, and a third copy lives in `graph-metadata.derived`. The `description.json` set is not the frontmatter set copied over. It is rebuilt by `spec-folder-extractor.ts:387-390` as `dedupe([...]).slice(0, 12)`, so it is capped at 12 entries and may legitimately differ from a longer curated frontmatter list. Today nothing checks that these three surfaces stay consistent, so a curated trigger that never reached the index, or a stale derived copy after a frontmatter edit, ships silently and degrades retrieval routing.",
